Aim/Skill map made by me, made for you.
Map info: A clean map, which I did while I had nothing to do, although I think the final result wasn't bad. It has long/short range shooting. I added a 3DSky but I didnt like it, so I tooked it out, it wouldn't make a big diference anyways :) Made for pubs with like 24 Slots, map has 18 Slots for each team. Well its a classic aim map, and all weapons are available.
Please Feedback and access I hope you like it, Enjoy it & Have Fun. Your friend - Unreal
